title: Eddie.Izzard.Unrepeatable.1994.x264.aac.mkv
description:
EDDIE IZZARD - UNREPEATABLE (1994) (MKV)

"If all the awards and nominations have gone to his head,
Izzard's performance does not show it. When he pulls up in 
mid-flow, there is the same sense you get with Robin 
Williams sometimes, of the audience racing to catch up
with a mind that moves too quickly for them."
-Independent

The DVD was recorded one night at the Albery Theatre in
March 1994, when Eddie Izzard was playing a limited seven
week sold-out run of his celebrated stand-up show.
